
The application is implemented using django framework, It uses in-memory data storage.
Search tool is implemented at "localhost:8000/tastysearch" where one can search for reviews containing one or more search terms.The results show top 20 matches that are present in the dataset and match best with the set of terms in the dataset.

In order to execute the application,the system requirements include Django-1.9 software.
The steps to run the application on your machine is as follows:
Clone the project and run the following command inside the project folder i.e. "tasty-search"

-tasty-search/$ ./manage.py runserver

This sets up a working instance of the project on "localhost:8000"

The search tool is in the following url: "localhost:8000/tastysearch/"